<h1 class="book big center">The Weekly Newsletter</h1>
<h2 class="center">Get useful tips and news about Stripe, Rails, and Ruby.</h2>

<p class="center">Join over 1,000 people who are interested in becoming better developers.</p>
<p class="center">Just enter your first name and email address below and click "Get updates!"</p>

<div class="center" style="margin-bottom: 3em">
  <form action="/subscribe" method="POST" class="form form-inline" style="margin-top: 0.5em;">
    <input type="text" class="sans" style="font-size: 17.5px; height: 36px; width: 8em; line-height: 22px;" name="name" placeholder="First name"></input>
    <input type="email" class="sans" style="font-size: 17.5px; height: 36px; width: 12em; line-height: 22px;" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com"></input>
    <input type="hidden" name="next" value="/newsletter-confirmed"></input>
    <input type="hidden" name="topic" value="<%= @app.params[:topic] %>"></input>
    <input class="btn btn-warning btn-large" type="submit" value="Get Updates!" />
  </form>
  <small>We won't send you spam. Unsubscribe at any time.</small>
</div>
